overview:
Doctor.com is a well-recognized brand in online health. Since its launch in 2008, the site has helped millions of people find, evaluate, and connect with the healthcare providers best suited to their unique needs.

Doctor.com’s database includes detailed profiles for more than 2 million doctors, dentists, nurses, therapists, and other health professionals in the United States. Users can search these profiles based on a wide variety of criteria such as location, specialty, accepted insurance, qualifications, board certification, and other factors. Users can also read detailed reviews and ratings written by other patients and are invited to share their own experiences.

Doctor.com also works with thousands of healthcare organizations of all sizes to optimize their online visibility, deploy online scheduling, streamline patient intake, and establish secure communications channels through which they can manage their patient relationships.

Doctor.com’s integrated platform is unique in that it combines deep patient-centric services for healthcare organizations with a targeted “supply” of millions of patients seeking care. The result is a unified platform designed to improve the entire lifecycle of healthcare interactions for all parties.
